data.description: Seller is very motivated and offering $5,000 Closing costs or rate buy down for any accepted offer. This 4 bed 2 baths home is in a quiet neighborhood of Kensington. Very close to May port, Jacksonville Beach and a lot of major restaurants and shopping mall. Nearby is St John's town center, Mayo hospital and UNF. This home has tiles flooring throughout the entire house. The roof just installed coupled of months ago. Well taken care home with an open floor plan. Make an appt. today. This house is price to sell.
